+                  + "support transactions. To fix this use an alternative metastore.",
+              e);
+        }
+
+        commitStatus = BaseMetastoreOperations.CommitStatus.UNKNOWN;
+        if (e.getMessage() != null
+            && e.getMessage()
+                .contains(
